Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:43.18,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fsp0}Will I see you again? {\fsp1}いつかすれ違う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:30.25,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr5 H-KL\fs62\fsp0}Sometimes I wonder again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.25,0:22:35.41,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr5 H-KL\fs62\fsp0}Sometimes I wonder again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.63,0:22:40.93,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}跨越数千年 接力棒传到我们手中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.93,0:22:45.43,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}因漫长道路而目眩 天旋地转
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:51.18,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一定有尚未发现的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:55.77,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}时刻都在这样思索 思索
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:23:00.90,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不惧失败 反复尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:06.81,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}哭着笑着 追寻光明
